  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-02 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This synthetic adversarial package embeds weakness W-EP-02: one ValidationResult (the most narratively detailed) carries no prov:wasGeneratedBy link to a generation Activity, breaking structured provenance while the prose narrative may mislead a reviewer into assuming the activity is adequately documented.",
